{"id":14109,"date":"2022-11-25T13:28:24","date_gmt":"2022-11-25T06:28:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14109"},"modified":"2022-11-25T13:44:39","modified_gmt":"2022-11-25T06:44:39","slug":"huong-dan-binh-chon-chuong-trinh-hyundai-du-ky","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/huong-dan-binh-chon-chuong-trinh-hyundai-du-ky\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u01af\u1edaNG D\u1eaaN B\u00ccNH CH\u1eccN CH\u01af\u01a0NG TR\u00ccNH HYUNDAI DU K\u00dd!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i! \u0110\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i! 3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cao cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 99.000.000 VN\u0110 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn: V\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft &#8211; b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn!<\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa! N\u00e0o l\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00ean th\u01a1 h\u00f9ng v\u0129, l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc c\u00e1c d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c Vi\u1ec7t Nam, l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed oai h\u00f9ng, l\u00e0 l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i, l\u00e0ng ngh\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, l\u00e0 m\u00f3n ngon \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng v\u00f9ng mi\u1ec1n\u2026 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u00fa v\u1ecb. C\u00e1c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u1ed3ng gh\u00e9p trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 bao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi g\u1eafm. Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng \u0111ang n\u00f4n nao t\u1eebng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb ngay c\u00f9ng qu\u00fd Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>Trong s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi v\u1ec1, Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 15 b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o V\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng khai.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9! Nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n b\u1ea1n! C\u00f9ng chia s\u1ebb v\u00e0 lan t\u1ecfa ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00fang ta. Nh\u1ea5n ga t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c xem v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn ngay th\u00f4i n\u00e0o!<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e1o h\u1ee9c qu\u00e1! Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac th\u1eadt th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn qua t\u1eebng l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn! C\u00f9ng du ngo\u1ea1n qua l\u0103ng k\u00ednh Hyundai v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nhau \u1edf cu\u1ed1i h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Th\u1eddi gian b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn:<\/strong> t\u1eeb 0h00 ng\u00e0y 24\/11\/2022 \u0111\u1ebfn 24h00 ng\u00e0y 26\/11\/2022.<\/li>\n<li><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch 1:<\/strong> Truy c\u1eadp website\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/vote.hyundai.thanhcong.vn\/\">https:\/\/vote.hyundai.thanhcong.vn<\/a> ho\u1eb7c<\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch 2:<\/strong> C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t\/c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Hyundai ME! b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u00e1ch d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/p>\n<p><strong>&#8211;<\/strong> Link c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t: \u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/hyundai.thanhcong.vn\/dich-vu-cskh\/ung-dung-hyundai-me\">https:\/\/hyundai.thanhcong.vn\/dich-vu-cskh\/ung-dung-hyundai-me<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>&#8211;<\/strong> Qu\u00e9t QR code \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t:<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/huong-dan-binh-chon-chuong-trinh-hyundai-du-ky\/qq\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-14113\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14113\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/QQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"498\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/QQ.png 498w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/QQ-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 498px) 100vw, 498px\" \/><\/a>&#8211; V\u00e0o AppStore\/CHPlay g\u00f5 Hyundai ME! \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; \u00a0<strong>Th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn:<\/strong> Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn 1 l\u1ea7n cho 1 b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn cho nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn may m\u1eafn:<\/strong> 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn may m\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n v\u1eadt r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn: b\u1ed1c th\u0103m may m\u1eafn theo s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn.<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u1eefng Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tham gia cu\u1ed9c thi v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m may m\u1eafn.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn:<\/strong> K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng c\u0103n c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng g\u1ed3m:<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>+ 01 Gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t: 40.000.000 VN\u0110<\/p>\n<p>+ 01 Gi\u1ea3i nh\u00ec: 20.000.000 VN\u0110<\/p>\n<p>+ 02 Gi\u1ea3i ba: 10.000.000 VN\u0110<\/p>\n<p>+ 03 Gi\u1ea3i khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch: M\u1ed7i gi\u1ea3i 3.000.000 VN\u0110<\/p>\n<p>+ 01 Gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t: 5.000.000 VN\u0110.<\/p>\n<p>+ 01 Gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng : 5.000.000 VN\u0110.<\/p>\n<p>+ Nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng c\u1ef1c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tham gia cu\u1ed9c thi c\u00f9ng 10 Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn may m\u1eafn.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/huong-dan-binh-chon-chuong-trinh-hyundai-du-ky\/z3909465367512_7e2e77dc4e4f886ca0c4cf2005cc7406\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-14115\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14115\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/z3909465367512_7e2e77dc4e4f886ca0c4cf2005cc7406.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1016\" height=\"1016\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/z3909465367512_7e2e77dc4e4f886ca0c4cf2005cc7406.jpg 1016w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/z3909465367512_7e2e77dc4e4f886ca0c4cf2005cc7406-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/z3909465367512_7e2e77dc4e4f886ca0c4cf2005cc7406-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/z3909465367512_7e2e77dc4e4f886ca0c4cf2005cc7406-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1016px) 100vw, 1016px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i! \u0110\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i! 3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cao cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng g